    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-11-09</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-12-12T18:23:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Secure Border Initiative Accountability Act of 2005 - Directs the Inspector General of the Department of Homeland Security to review each contract action related to the Department's Secure Border Initiative having a value greater than $20 million to determine whether such action fully complies with applicable cost requirements, performance objectives, program milestones, and timelines. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
